 https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_tyresegibson_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_tyresegibson_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/2023_tyresegibson_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/fast-and-furious"><em>《速度与激情》</em></a>明星泰瑞斯·吉布森因涉嫌种族歧视而起诉美国五金店家得宝 (The Home Depot)，索赔超过 100 万美元（合 79 万英镑）。</p><p>这位曾出演过七部大片的演员声称，他和两名同事在二月份的一次事件中遭受了“令人发指的歧视性虐待”。</p><p>本周早些时候在洛杉矶提起的一项诉讼详细说明了据称发生在洛杉矶县西山家得宝商店的事件。</p><p>据<a href="https://variety.com/2023/film/news/tyrese-gibson-sues-home-depot-racial-profiling-1235694090/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a>报道，这起事件涉及吉布森、埃里克·莫拉和曼努埃尔·埃尔南德斯，他们因“据称的系统故障”而被拘留。</p><p>三人投诉称，这导致他们在大约 20 分钟内无法结帐，然后结账台周围开始出现人群。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cvzj1j4ASCx/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3