ands <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f605.png" alt="😅" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a title="徒步战士" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/foofighters?refer=embed">#foofighters</a> <a title="达韦格罗尔" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/davegrohl?refer=embed">#davegrohl</a> <a title="迈克尔布雷" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/michaelbuble?refer=embed">#michaelbuble</a> <a title="域外" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/outsidelands?refer=embed">#outsidelands</a> <a title="节日" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/festivals?refer=embed">#festivals</a> <a title="现场音乐" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/livemusic?refer=embed">#livemusic</a> <a title="音乐会" target="_blank" href="https://www.tiktok.com/tag/concerts?refer=embed">#concerts</a></p><p> <a target="_blank" title="♬ 原声 - 结果" href="https://www.tiktok.com/music/original-sound-7266679494092819246?refer=embed">♬ 原始声音 – 结果</a></section></blockquote><p><script async src="https://www.tiktok.com/embed.js"></script></p><p> 表演结束后，格罗尔说：“天哪，这是迈克尔·布布尔”，然后补充道：“我们一直在做这样的事情，观众中的人们上前说‘我知道那首该死的歌’，然后他们走上前去，然后他们知道第一节，但他们不知道。</p><p> “所以这个混蛋——我不是在开玩笑——今天从阿根廷飞来，他妈的给你们唱这首歌。因为玩笑再开也不过分。”</p><p>此前，已故鼓手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-hawkins">泰勒·霍金斯的儿子肖恩·霍金斯</a>最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-hawkins-son-shane-performs-led-zeppelin-black-sabbath-with-chevy-metal-3478262">与雪佛兰金属公司一起登上舞台，上周在加利福尼亚州进行了几场演出</a>。</p><p>这位 17 岁的年轻人走上舞台，坐在设备后面参加了他父亲在加利福尼亚州自己的翻唱乐队最近的两场演出，表演了摇滚经典，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">Black Sabbath</a>的“The Wizard”和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/led-zeppelin">Led Zeppelin</a> 1969 年的热门歌曲“Moby”迪克。</p><p>与此同时，Foo Fighters 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alanis-morissette">Alanis Morissette</a>最近在日本富士摇滚音乐节上翻唱了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighers-and-alanis-morissette-honour-sinead-oconnor-with-mandinka-cover-3475206">《Mandinka》</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-irish-music-legend-dies-aged-56-3473863">向上个月去世、享年 56 岁的</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sinead-oconnor">Sinéad O&#39;Connor</a>致敬。</p><p>该<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighters-uk-tour-pre-sale-saw-unprecedented-demand-3462929">乐队计划明年前往英国巡演</a>。您可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Ffoo-fighters-tickets%2Fartist%2F776005">在这里</a>购买剩余的门票。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-foo-fighters-team-up-with-michael-buble-for-havent-met-you-yet-3482065">Watch Foo Fighters 与 Michael Bublé 合作的《Haven&#39;t Met You Yet》</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
